parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate odometer and fuel gauge can cause safety concerns, especially when driving on the interstate, as it can lead to unexpected running out of gas, which can cause accidents.
symptoms: Odometer reading changes even when not driving
inaccurate fuel gauge reading
uncertainty about the actual mileage and fuel level.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning radio can cause safety concerns, especially in emergency situations, as it can prevent the use of OnStar services.
symptoms: Radio turns off and on randomly
gets stuck after Bluetooth phone calls
screen goes black without warning
loss of all functions through the radio screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's reliability and safety concerns can put the driver's life in danger, especially when experiencing issues such as white exhaust blowing from the vents, battery problems, and unaddressed maintenance issues.
symptoms: White exhaust blowing from the vents
battery problems
unaddressed maintenance issues
vehicle not starting
pliers left under the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning window switches can cause inconvenience and safety concerns, especially when driving.
symptoms: Window switches not rolling up or down
no clicking noise when pushing the switch
acting like it's not getting an electric signal to the switches.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The CAM shaft issues can cause the engine check light to remain on, potentially leading to engine damage, decreased performance, and reduced fuel efficiency.
symptoms: The engine check light remains on
the vehicle's engine performance is decreased
the vehicle's fuel efficiency is reduced
the CAM shaft is faulty or malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to address recall issues can lead to ongoing problems with the vehicle, potentially causing safety risks, decreased performance, and reduced fuel efficiency.
symptoms: The dealership fails to repair or replace recalled parts
the vehicle's issues persist despite multiple visits to the dealership
the owner is not informed about recall notices.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deactivation of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the passenger will not be protected by the airbag.
